---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Technically Within Parameters is a 25–60 player sci-fi megagame package from YEG Megagames."
    />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Technically Within Parameters | YEG Megagames Store</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/cropped-iconpng.png" />
  </head>

  <body class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-100">
    <main class="min-h-screen">
      <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-yellow-400/20 bg-slate-950/90 backdrop-blur">
        <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-5 py-4">
          <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 no-underline">
            <img src="/img/cropped-iconpng.png" alt="" class="h-10 w-10" />
            <span class="text-xl font-black tracking-wide text-yellow-300">YEG Megagames</span>
          </a>

          <nav class="hidden gap-6 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-300 md:flex">
            <a class="no-underline hover:text-yellow-300" href="/">Home</a>
            <a class="no-underline hover:text-yellow-300" href="/#events">Events</a>
            <a class="no-underline text-yellow-300" href="/store-twp">Store</a>
            <a class="no-underline hover:text-yellow-300" href="https://discord.gg/gpVh2X6sKu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Discord</a>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-yellow-400/20">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(2,6,23,.72),rgba(2,6,23,.94)),url('/img/twpbackground.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,rgba(56,189,248,.22),transparent_34%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_right,rgba(250,204,21,.18),transparent_38%)]"></div>

        <div class="relative mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-5 py-20 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr] lg:items-center lg:py-28">
          <section>
            <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-yellow-300">
              Megagame Store
            </p>

            <h1 class="max-w-4xl text-5xl font-black leading-none text-white sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
              Technically Within Parameters
            </h1>

            <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-xl leading-8 text-slate-200">
              The Reliant is held together with duct tape, poor decisions,
              and corporate negligence. Can your crew survive the shift?
            </p>

            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-yellow-300/40 bg-slate-950/85 px-5 py-3 shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-yellow-300">Digital package</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-3xl font-black text-white">$200 CAD</p>
              </div>

              <a
                href="#buy"
                class="rounded-md bg-yellow-400 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-950 no-underline shadow-lg hover:bg-yellow-300"
              >
                Purchase TWP
              </a>

              <a
                href="https://discord.gg/gpVh2X6sKu"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="rounded-md border border-sky-300/70 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-200 no-underline hover:bg-sky-300/10"
              >
                Ask on Discord
              </a>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="rounded-2xl border border-sky-300/20 bg-slate-900/95 p-6 shadow-2xl shadow-black/60 backdrop-blur">
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-yellow-400/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 via-slate-200 to-slate-400">
              <img
                src="/img/twp-logo.png"
                alt="Technically Within Parameters"
                class="h-80 w-full object-contain p-6"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-4">
              <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700 bg-slate-950 p-3 text-center">
                <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-yellow-300">Players</p>
                <p class="mt-1 font-bold text-white">25–60</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700 bg-slate-950 p-3 text-center">
                <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-yellow-300">Length</p>
                <p class="mt-1 font-bold text-white">5–7 hrs</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700 bg-slate-950 p-3 text-center">
                <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-yellow-300">Theme</p>
                <p class="mt-1 font-bold text-white">Sci-fi chaos</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700 bg-slate-950 p-3 text-center">
                <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-yellow-300">Format</p>
                <p class="mt-1 font-bold text-white">Digital</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="buy" class="bg-slate-900 px-5 py-16 lg:py-20">
        <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.8fr]">
          <article class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-sky-300/20 bg-slate-950 shadow-2xl shadow-black/50">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 via-slate-200 to-slate-400">
              <img
                src="/img/twp-logo.png"
                alt="Technically Within Parameters"
                class="h-80 w-full object-contain p-6"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="p-8">
              <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-yellow-300">
                Digital Megagame Package
              </p>

              <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white">
                A sci-fi workplace megagame of shipboard chaos, side hustles, and questionable ethics.
              </h2>

              <p class="mt-5 leading-8 text-slate-300">
                Welcome aboard the Reliant — or, as the crew call her, the
                (un)Reliant. Players take on crew roles ranging from Captain
                to Clown as they attempt to keep the ship running long enough
                to finish their shift.
              </p>

              <p class="mt-5 leading-8 text-slate-300">
                You might be mining asteroids, transporting dangerous material,
                keeping the engines alive, managing emergencies, or trying to stop
                a suspicious biology sample from becoming everyone’s problem.
              </p>

              <p class="mt-5 leading-8 text-slate-300">
                Technically Within Parameters combines megagaming, roleplay,
                negotiation, resource management, real-time crisis management,
                shipboard departments, space operations, emergencies, combat,
                trading, and questionable ethics into one fast-paced day-long event.
              </p>

              <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-900 p-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white">What the package includes</h3>

                <ul class="mt-5 grid gap-3 text-slate-300 md:grid-cols-2">
                  <li>✓ Core rulebook</li>
                  <li>✓ Printable role sheets</li>
                  <li>✓ Department materials</li>
                  <li>✓ Station cards and sheets</li>
                  <li>✓ Control documents</li>
                  <li>✓ Setup guide</li>
                  <li>✓ Player handouts</li>
                  <li>✓ Event assets</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-8 rounded-2xl border border-yellow-300/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400/15 to-slate-900 p-6">
                <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-yellow-300">Purchase price</p>
                <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-4">
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-5xl font-black text-white">$200 CAD</p>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">One-time payment for the complete digital game package.</p>
                  </div>

                  <a
                    href="https://paypal.me/TechnicallyWP"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="rounded-md bg-yellow-400 px-7 py-4 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-950 no-underline shadow-lg hover:bg-yellow-300"
                  >
                    Pay $200 CAD with PayPal
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-4">

                <a
                  href="https://discord.gg/gpVh2X6sKu"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="rounded-md border border-sky-300/70 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-200 no-underline hover:bg-sky-300/10"
                >
                  Ask About TWP
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <aside class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-950 p-8 shadow-xl shadow-black/40">
            <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-yellow-300">How it works</p>
            <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-black text-white">Pay, confirm, and receive your game</h2>

            <ol class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-slate-300">
              <li class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
                <span class="font-black text-yellow-300">1.</span>
                Send <strong class="text-white">$200 CAD</strong> through the PayPal payment link.
              </li>

              <li class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
                <span class="font-black text-yellow-300">2.</span>
                In the PayPal payment note, include <strong class="text-white">TWP Purchase</strong> and the email address where you want the game delivered.
              </li>

              <li class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
                <span class="font-black text-yellow-300">3.</span>
                After the completed payment is verified, you will receive a private Google Drive folder link by email.
              </li>
            </ol>

            <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl border border-yellow-400/20 bg-yellow-400/10 p-5">
              <p class="font-bold text-yellow-200">
                Payments are confirmed through the PayPal account connected to paypal.me/TechnicallyWP. Please make sure the payment shows as completed and that your delivery email is included in the note.
              </p>
            </div>


            <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-900 p-5">
              <h3 class="font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-white">Delivery timing</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-300">
                Google Drive access is sent manually after payment verification. Please allow up to one business day for delivery.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl border border-sky-300/20 bg-sky-300/10 p-5">
              <h3 class="font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-200">
                Want to run it first?
              </h3>

              <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-300">
                Join the Discord to ask about playtesting, running the game,
                or adapting it for your local group.
              </p>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer class="border-t border-yellow-400/20 bg-slate-950 px-5 py-8 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">
        <p>YEG Megagames · Edmonton, Alberta</p>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
